Get-Help	
    - Learn how a command works.

Get-Command	
    - Find available commands.

Where-Object	  
    - Filter objects based on conditions.

Select-Object	
    - Choose specific properties to display.

Sort-Object	
    - Sort output alphabetically or numerically.

Group-Object	
    - Group similar objects together.

Measure-Object	
    - Count, sum, average, or measure data.

ForEach-Object	
    - Perform an action on every object in a pipeline.

Out-GridView	
    - Display results in a searchable GUI table (Windows PowerShell).

Export-Csv	
    - Export data to Excel-compatible CSV files.

Import-Csv	
    - Read CSV files into PowerShell objects.

Compare-Object	
    - Compare two lists and identify differences.

Tee-Object	
    - Send output to both the screen and a file simultaneously.
